BC UpdateCache extension README

What is the BC UpdateCache extension?
================================

BC UpdateCache is a true eZ publish extension
that provides module view to update node cache for eZ Publish

This extension is created as an automated way to regenerate
caches after you have cleared all cache. The module view
/updatecache/cache performes multiple GET requests to 
all pages in a subtree specified when starting the module.
This means you do not need to manually click though all
the pages to generate caches for them.


BC UpdateCache version
=======================

The current version of BC UpdateCache is 0.0.2
Last Major update: November 21, 2011

You can find details about changes for this
version in doc/changelogs/CHANGELOG-0.0.2


